[Course_Description]
As construction professionals continue to shift from paper-based to digital management processes, the easy-to-use PlanGrid construction software is proving itself to be an industry leader. This advanced course teaches construction managers how to take advantage of several key PlanGrid features and leverage this construction productivity software to accomplish a variety of management activities more efficiently. Instructor Jim Rogers shows how to use functionality that allows you to track and manage project reports. Plus, learn how to use PlanGrid features to improve communication among team members—including how to create workspaces and access them on mobile apps—as well as aggregate data collection to monitor project health.